# Redirects for SEO - Netlify/Vercel/Cloudflare compatible
# All redirects use 301 (permanent) for SEO benefit

# Priority 1: HTTP www to HTTPS non-www (direct redirect, no chain)
http://www.wordcounterplusapp.com/*  https://wordcounterplusapp.com/:splat  301!

# Priority 2: HTTPS www to HTTPS non-www (permanent redirect)
https://www.wordcounterplusapp.com/*  https://wordcounterplusapp.com/:splat  301!

# Priority 3: HTTP non-www to HTTPS non-www
http://wordcounterplusapp.com/*  https://wordcounterplusapp.com/:splat  301!

# Remove trailing slashes for consistency (except root)
https://wordcounterplusapp.com/*/  https://wordcounterplusapp.com/:splat  301!

# Fallback for SPA (must be last)
/*  /index.html  200
